			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><P align=justify>The Test Server has been updated with the maintenance patch for the Throne of Oblivion update. Here is a list of changes:</P>
<br />
<P align=justify><B>WORLD</B></P>
<br />
<UL>
<br />
<LI>Added Unarmed Weapons to the Weaponsmiths in the Hamlets and starting Safeholds 
<br />
<LI>City Population has been reimplemented on the mouse-over</LI></UL>
<br />
<P align=justify><B>RACE</B></P>
<br />
<UL>
<br />
<LI>The Irekei Racerune no longer included "increased UA damage" on the mouseover 
<br />
<LI>Fortitude powers now have a 60 second recycle timer</LI></UL>
<br />
<P align=justify><B>CLASS</B></P>
<br />
<UL>
<br />
<LI>Increased the Sword Power Ranking for Rangers 
<br />
<LI>The Necromancer Pet Summon ability can no longer be interrupted 
<br />
<LI>The Wings of the Seraphim's poweraction sort order has been updated</LI></UL>
<br />
<P align=justify><B>DISCIPLINE</B></P>
<br />
<UL>
<br />
<LI>The Drannok Attack Speed Debuff has been changed to an instacast power 
<br />
<LI>Fortitude powers now have a 60 second recycle timer</LI></UL>
<br />
<P align=justify><B>REALM</B></P>
<br />
<UL>
<br />
<LI>The reclaim timer for Realms now persists through server downtimes 
<br />
<LI>Updated the text description on the Realm Charters 
<br />
<LI>The Session Log will now contain an Error Message when taxing a city for 0%</LI></UL>
<br />
<P align=justify><B>CITY/SIEGE</B></P>
<br />
<UL>
<br />
<LI>Members who do not belong to a warring Nation can no longer be friended to Buildings of War 
<br />
<LI>If an attacker or defender falls under the limit of Buildings of War they can now be replaced 
<br />
<LI>The Information Window on the Runemaster will now dynamically update when removing structures from the protection list 
<br />
<LI>Vampire and Lizardmen Hirelings now use a new naming convention (this only works on new hirelings) 
<br />
<LI>The Strongbox information now updates dynamically when upgrading a Hireling 
<br />
<LI>Updated the Hireling and Artillery Captain Windows for ease of use 
<br />
<LI>The refund process has been adjusted for Rank 0 buildings </LI></UL>
<br />
<P align=justify><B>CRAFTING</B></P>
<br />
<UL>
<br />
<LI>An error has been fixed now allowing players to produce multiple random magic 
<br />
<LI>Add a button that gives players the option to fill all seven slots with the same type of item 
<br />
<LI>Added a Cancel Button to the Recycle or Complete confirmation window</LI></UL>
<br />
<P align=justify><B>GENERAL</B></P>
<br />
<UL>
<br />
<LI>Added optimizations to the terrain and structure loading system 
<br />
<LI>Monsters that would not leave a corpse will now do so (such as Air Elementals) 
<br />
<LI>Added new ambient sounds</LI></UL>
<br />
<P align=justify></P>
<br />

<br />
------------------------------------------
<br />

<br />
Not sure when it comes to live servers, but I would assume within the next week or two.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold">[ Justin ][ 59 Human Bard ] [ Wrath ] 
