				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This went in yesterday around 3PM EST.  The forge screens are pretty much exactly as they were posted in the other thread.   I did some rolling on the sages in IA last night [just for the fast completion times] and while the system still sucks, it is much easier now.
<br />

<br />
I also noted the corpses on wraiths and reapers, which makes camping traveler a little more profitable.  Not that I ever need to, I just run by, he's usually there [85% success rate at this point] and I whack him.  But now when you pull the entire camp, you'll have some bodies to loot.
<br />

<br />
Nothing else special beyond that.
<br />

<br />
On an unrelated note, I've had four offers to sell me cities in the last 36 hours.  I'd say the rats are rapidly abandoning this sinking ship.  Of course, once the dam breaks they will not be even offering to sell things and just disappearing.<br />_________________<br /><strong>Shadowbane</strong>
